title: rules for being a gal on the go with eli rallo
itunes:title: rules for being a gal on the go with eli rallo
description:
Brooke and Danielle are joined by Eli Rallo (better known as thejarr online) to discuss “the rules” for being a gal on the go!  Eli is the queen of rules, so it was only fitting to have her on to discuss this topic.  The gals get into rules for travel, what to carry in your tote bag and even how to fit more into your day.  Be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies and stories!
